Super old school.

00:35.035 --> 00:37.037
Like, middle school.

00:37.138 --> 00:38.506
[laughs]

00:38.606 --> 00:40.908
Yep, just about right--
right around there.

00:41.008 --> 00:42.910
Hey, I remember when
this game came out, man,

00:43.010 --> 00:44.412
I didn't even skate
or anything.

00:44.512 --> 00:46.046
I used to skateboard
when I was a kid.

00:46.147 --> 00:47.248
I was pretty decent too.

00:47.348 --> 00:49.383
Oh, yeah?
I love that.

00:49.483 --> 00:51.385
