Hey, Liza's turn.

01:11.872 --> 01:13.507
Oh, no, no, it's okay.
I don't play video games.

01:13.607 --> 01:14.708
What do you mean?

01:14.808 --> 01:16.877
My parents didn't
allow them.

01:16.977 --> 01:18.446
That's, like,
child abuse.

01:18.546 --> 01:21.282
I mean, you've played
something though, right?

01:21.382 --> 01:22.950
Like, Mario Kart
at a friend's house.

01:23.050 --> 01:24.285
No, I haven't.

01:24.385 --> 01:25.853
What about, like,
Candy Crush?

01:25.953 --> 01:27.555
Sorry.

01:27.655 --> 01:29.923
