02:05.426 --> 02:06.560
Yeah.

02:06.660 --> 02:12.400
It's all yours, big guy.

02:12.500 --> 02:13.801
What happened to the door?

02:13.901 --> 02:15.903
Oh, we--
we broke it wrestling.

02:16.003 --> 02:17.405
We're using it
as a table.

02:17.505 --> 02:19.039
You should've
totally been there.

02:19.207 --> 02:20.441
Next time.

02:20.541 --> 02:21.742
We can't.
They're right there.

02:21.842 --> 02:23.577
They're fine.

02:23.677 --> 02:25.213
They won't lift their heads
from that game for hours.

02:25.313 --> 02:26.714
It's fine, it's fine.

02:26.814 --> 02:28.749
All right, I think
I'm gonna take a rain check.

02:28.849 --> 02:30.083
Or a door check.

02:30.218 --> 02:31.385
Or we could go
check the shower.

02:31.485 --> 02:33.621
Mm, you have mushrooms
growing on the tub.

02:33.721 --> 02:35.589
It's okay.

02:35.689 --> 02:37.991
I really do have a big day
at work tomorrow.

02:38.091 --> 02:39.727
Work is a four-letter word.

