are in, like, an hour.

09:24.397 --> 09:25.633
I just don't--

09:25.699 --> 09:26.800
[knock on door]

09:26.900 --> 09:28.235
Oh, here you are.

09:28.335 --> 09:29.737
In an entirely
different department

09:29.837 --> 09:31.371
than the one
that employs you.

09:31.471 --> 09:33.106
