and your SPANX.

09:40.547 --> 09:41.649
Shh, shh, shh.
Charles.

09:41.715 --> 09:43.784
Hi. Hi, Dana.

09:43.884 --> 09:45.786
And Liza, right?

09:45.886 --> 09:47.220
Right.

09:47.320 --> 09:49.089
Looking forward to
the PEN awards tonight?

09:49.189 --> 09:51.992
Yeah, I am looking forward
to seeing the Knopf table

09:52.092 --> 09:54.662
