Bjornberg.

09:54.695 --> 09:57.097
Maybe we can share
a town car over.

09:57.197 --> 09:59.466
I can't. I have to go home
and meet the new babysitter.

09:59.566 --> 10:02.435
Oh, I understand.
Well, see you there.

10:02.535 --> 10:03.871
Yep.

10:05.272 --> 10:06.774
Is he looking?

10:06.874 --> 10:08.408
He sure is.

10:08.508 --> 10:10.443
No, don't look.
You'll ruin the moment.

10:16.516 --> 10:18.085
Did you make sure I was
seated next to him?

10:18.185 --> 10:19.086
Weeks ago.

10:19.186 --> 10:20.087
Did you--

10:20.187 --> 10:21.488
I reconfirmed it
today.

10:21.588 --> 10:23.356
I feel sorry for him
about the divorce,

10:23.456 --> 10:25.358
but I can't say I'm not thrilled
he's on the market.

10:25.458 --> 10:26.526
He does seem nice.

10:26.626 --> 10:28.528
Nice?
Are you kidding me?

10:28.628 --> 10:31.031
He's straight, handsome,
intellectual, and available.

10:31.131 --> 10:32.766
Do you realize
how rare that is?

10:32.866 --> 10:34.835
It's like finding a snow leopard
in your backyard.

10:34.935 --> 10:36.937
Oh, come on.
It's not that bad.

10:37.037 --> 10:39.372
You have no idea what it's like
to be single and in your 40s.

10:39.472 --> 10:41.508
It's like trying to rent out
a beautiful apartment

10:41.608 --> 10:43.376
where a murder took place--
everyone's spooked.

10:43.476 --> 10:46.279
I kick myself for all those
years I wasted with Philip Roth.

10:46.379 --> 10:48.515
Have I mentioned that I was
involved with Philip Roth?

10:48.615 --> 10:50.383
Several times.

10:50.483 --> 10:51.985
I was.

10:53.887 --> 10:55.055
Hey.

10:55.155 --> 10:57.090
I hate being 26.

10:57.190 --> 10:58.558
What happened?

10:58.658 --> 10:59.893
Should I start
with how I had

10:59.993 --> 11:01.729
to pluck a chin hair
from my boss' face,

11:01.795 --> 11:04.197
or perhaps you'd like to hear
how I was accused of adultery

11:04.297 --> 11:06.934
and whacked with a rolled-up
manuscript?

11:07.034 --> 11:08.635
What?

11:08.736 --> 11:10.804
I just don't know if I could
go through all this again.

11:10.904 --> 11:12.205
It's so demeaning.

11:12.305 --> 11:16.476
All the grunt work
and all the lying.

11:16.576 --> 11:18.511
I honestly don't know
if I can do this anymore.

11:18.611 --> 11:20.547
Well, you need
the money.

11:20.647 --> 11:22.382
And there's perks
to being 26,

11:22.482 --> 11:25.185
